name: Beef Kebab

instructionRequests.step: Mix the meat with soy sauce, minced garlic and salt
Cut onion and green pepper in 1-inch squares
Arrange meat, onion, green pepper and grape tomatoes onto the skewers
Take it to the barbecue grill for 20 min (10 each side) or until meat is as you like

note: You can use your beef of preference in cubes
additionalInfo: These kebabs are so good! I first made them to go camping. My friends were going to barbecue but I wanted something different than just meat and burguers. So, I did the kebabs a few days before and kept them on the freezer.
